    <title>About StoreJS</title>
    <style>
      body { background: #0d1117; color: #c9d1d9; font-family: monospace; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
      pre { color: #58a6ff; font-size: 10px; line-height: 1.1; }
